### ----------------------------------------
### List Wellness Logs (all)
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wellness
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----------------------------------------
### List filtered by bodyPartProfile
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wellness?bodyPartProfileId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----------------------------------------
### List within date range
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wellness?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----------------------------------------
### List with limit
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wellness?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----------------------------------------
### List with date + bodyPartProfile + limit
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wellness?bodyPartProfileId=1&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

